text: Elliptical may mean: * having the shape of an ellipse, or more broadly, any oval shape ** in botany, having an elliptic leaf shape ** of aircraft wings, having an elliptical planform * characterised by ellipsis (the omission of words), or by concision more broadly * an elliptical trainer, an exercise machine == See also == * Ellipse (disambiguation) * Ellipsis (disambiguation)
title: Elliptical
